{
  "stem": "22944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they tried to keep our family together the best way they could and some kind of normality.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, they knew that things are already bad, and I only found out much later when I was older.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was sort of a lot of commotion going-- coming and going-- and changes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't explain to us why we have to move from one district to another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But obviously, I knew afterwards-- the reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last home in Bratislava that we lived-- I've got fairly strong memories, and it was not a very happy place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in a-- in one part of the Judenstrasse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, it's-- Judenstrasse was the street of-- the Jewish street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived in kind of a cottage, and it was few rooms in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had shutters-- wooden shutters-- because many drunkards and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] young Hitler movement started to develop those days, and they used to throw bottles and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember that we used to go find a place quite early in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we still had a maid, I remember, even in that place, because our maid was so well-trained by my late mother and father.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She used to always insist, before I eat, I wash my hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she used a blessing and grace after meal and morning prayers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was well-trained.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I would not know 100%, as I-- as I was the youngest of the family, but I think we probably had to go to live there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't a ghetto in such that there was gates, like in Venice.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
